Stage 1
Collect 3 digit number from user
Get the first, second and last digit
Add the three digits
Display the three digits

Stage 2
Prompt user to input a number between 0 to 1000
Collect the number from user
Store the number in a variable digitA
Perform digitA / 100 to get first Digit 
Save the first Digit in a variable firstNo
Perform DigitA % 10 to get last Digit
Save the third Digit in a variable lastNo
Perform digitA / 10 to get the first 2 Digit 
Save the 2 first Digit in a variable tosec
Perform tosec % 10 to get second Digit 
Save the second Digit in a variable SecondNo

